{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 20''' is the 20th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . == Events == * {{ill|Kenkou|ja|建光|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|121|ja|121st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 19|ja|10月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The oldest Chinese dictionary, ''{{ill|Shuowen Jiezi|ja|説文解字|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} '', compiled by {{ill|Xu Shen|ja|許慎|lt=Xu Shen|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , was presented to Emperor {{ill|An|ja|安帝|lt=Emperor An|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of the Later Han. * {{ill|Bunji|ja|文治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1187|ja|1187th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara Toshinari|ja|藤原俊成|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} presented the anthology ''{{ill|Senzaishū|ja|千載和歌集|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} '' to {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|後白河法皇|lt=Emperor Go-Shirakawa|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * {{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd Year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1331|ja|1331st year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgon|ja|光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Kōgon|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of the Northern Court ascended the throne. * {{ill|Bunwa|ja|文和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd Year / {{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1353|ja|1353rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 17|ja|10月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} entered Kyoto, endorsing the authority of {{ill|Emperor Gōkō|ja|後光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Gōkō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – Emperor {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} departed Kyoto and headed for Tokyo.
== Births == * {{ill|Tenmon|ja|天文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1535|ja|1535th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Niwa Nagahide|ja|丹羽長秀|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a military commander (died {{ill|1585|ja|1585th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1852|ja|1852nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Honinbo Shuei|ja|本因坊秀栄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a professional Go player (died {{ill|1907|ja|1907th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
