2=draft}} 15th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1730|ja|1730th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 31|ja|10月31日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Naka Jinbe|ja|中甚兵衛|lt=Naka Jinbe|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a village head from Imaze Village in Kawachi Province who significantly contributed to the reorganization of work on the Yamato River (born {{ill|1639|ja|1639th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Bunka|ja|文化|1=Bunka|2=ja|3=文化 (元号)|4=de|5=Bunka (Ära)|6=ko|7=분카|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1806|ja|1806年|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 31|ja|10月31日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kitagawa Utamaro|ja|喜多川歌麿|lt=Kitagawa Utamaro|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , an ukiyo-e artist (born {{ill|1753|ja|1753rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
