{{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 20''' is the 20th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . == Events == * {{ill|Kenkou|ja|建光|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|121|ja|121st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 19|ja|10月19日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – The oldest Chinese dictionary, ''{{ill|Shuowen Jiezi|ja|説文解字|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} '', compiled by {{ill|Xu Shen|ja|許慎|lt=Xu Shen|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , was presented to Emperor {{ill|An|ja|安帝|lt=Emperor An|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of the Later Han. * {{ill|Bunji|ja|文治|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1187|ja|1187th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara Toshinari|ja|藤原俊成|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} presented the anthology ''{{ill|Senzaishū|ja|千載和歌集|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} '' to {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|後白河法皇|lt=Emperor Go-Shirakawa|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . * {{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd Year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1331|ja|1331st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgon|ja|光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Kōgon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of the Northern Court ascended the throne. * {{ill|Bunwa|ja|文和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd Year / {{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 8th Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1353|ja|1353rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 17|ja|10月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} entered Kyoto, endorsing the authority of {{ill|Emperor Gōkō|ja|後光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Gōkō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – Emperor {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} departed Kyoto and headed for Tokyo.
== Births == * {{ill|Tenmon|ja|天文|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 4th Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1535|ja|1535th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Niwa Nagahide|ja|丹羽長秀|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a military commander (died {{ill|1585|ja|1585th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1852|ja|1852nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Honinbo Shuei|ja|本因坊秀栄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a professional Go player (died {{ill|1907|ja|1907th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
