q=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 31|ja|10月31日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Naka Jinbe|ja|中甚兵衛|lt=Naka Jinbe|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a village head from Imaze Village in Kawachi Province who significantly contributed to the reorganization of work on the Yamato River (born {{ill|1639|ja|1639th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Bunka|ja|文化|1=Bunka|2=ja|3=文化 (元号)|4=de|5=Bunka (Ära)|6=ko|7=분카|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1806|ja|1806年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 31|ja|10月31日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Kitagawa Utamaro|ja|喜多川歌麿|lt=Kitagawa Utamaro|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , an ukiyo-e artist (born {{ill|1753|ja|1753rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
