{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月二十|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 20일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 20''' is the 20th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . == Events == * {{ill|Kenkou|ja|建光|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|121|ja|121st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 19|ja|10月19日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – The oldest Chinese dictionary, ''{{ill|Shuowen Jiezi|ja|説文解字|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} '', compiled by {{ill|Xu Shen|ja|許慎|lt=Xu Shen|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , was presented to Emperor {{ill|An|ja|安帝|lt=Emperor An|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of the Later Han. * {{ill|Bunji|ja|文治|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1187|ja|1187th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara Toshinari|ja|藤原俊成|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} presented the anthology ''{{ill|Senzaishū|ja|千載和歌集|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} '' to {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|後白河法皇|lt=Emperor Go-Shirakawa|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . * {{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd Year / {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1331|ja|1331st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgon|ja|光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Kōgon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} of the Northern Court ascended the throne. * {{ill|Bunwa|ja|文和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd Year / {{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 8th Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1353|ja|1353rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 17|ja|10月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} entered Kyoto, endorsing the authority of {{ill|Emperor Gōkō|ja|後光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Gōkō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – Emperor {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} departed Kyoto and headed for Tokyo.
