draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1331|qq=}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 22|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kōgon|ja|光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Kōgon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Kōgon|qq=}} of the Northern Court ascended the throne. * {{ill|Bunwa|ja|文和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunwa|qq=}} 2nd Year / {{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōhei|qq=}} 8th Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1353|ja|1353rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1353|qq=}} {{ill|October 17|ja|10月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 17|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Takauji|qq=}} entered Kyoto, endorsing the authority of {{ill|Emperor Gōkō|ja|後光厳天皇|lt=Emperor Gōkō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Gōkō|qq=}} . * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1868|qq=}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 4|qq=}} ) – Emperor {{ill|M