mple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Go-Shirakawa|qq=}} . * [[:en:Gentoku|Gentoku]] 3rd Year / [[:en:Genkō (1331–1334)|Genkō]] 1st Year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1331|1331]] [[:en:October 22|October 22]] ) – [[:en:Emperor Kōgon|Emperor Kōgon]] of the Northern Court ascended the throne. * [[:en:Bunna|Bunwa]] 2nd Year / [[:en:Zhengping|Shōhei]] 8th Year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1353|1353]] [[:en:October 17|October 17]] ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Takauji|qq=}} entered Kyoto, endorsing the authority of [[:en:Emperor Go-Kōgon|Emperor Gōkō]] . * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 1st Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1868|1868]] [[:en:November 4|November 4]] ) – Emperor [[:en:Emperor Meiji|Meiji]] departed Kyoto and headed for Tokyo.
