== Births == * {{ill|Tenmon|ja|天文|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenmon|qq=}} 4th Year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1535|1535]] [[:en:October 16|October 16]] ) – [[:en:Niwa Nagahide|Niwa Nagahide]] , a military commander (died [[:en:1585|1585]] ). * [[:en:Kaei|Kaei]] 5th Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1852|1852]] [[:en:November 1|November 1]] ) – [[:en:Hon'inbō Shūei|Honinbo Shuei]] , a professional Go player (died [[:en:1907|1907]] ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Genki|ja|Genki (era)|Genki|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genki|qq=}} 1st Year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1570|1570]] [[:en:October 19|October 19]] ) – [[:en:Mori Yoshinari|Mori Kanenari]] , a military commander (born [[:en:1523|1523]] ). * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 10th Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1605|1605]] [[:en:November 1|November 1]] ) – [[:en:Yamauchi Kazutoyo|Yamauchi Kazutoyo]] , the first lord of the Tosa Domain (born [[:en:1546|1546]] ). * [[:en:Jōō (Edo period)|Shōō]] 3rd Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1654|1654]] [[:en:October 30|October 30]] ) – [[:en:Emperor Go-Kōmyō|Emperor Gōmyō]] , the 110th Emperor (born [[:en:1633|1633]] ). * [[:en:Kyōhō|Kyōhō]] 15th Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1730|1730]] [[:en:October 31|October 31]] ) – {{ill|Naka Jinbe|ja|中甚兵衛|lt=Naka Jinbe|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Naka Jinbe|qq=}} , a village head from Imaze Village in Kawachi Province who significantly contributed to the reorganization of work on the Yamato River (born [[:en:1639|1639]] ). * [[:en:Culture|Bunka]] 3rd Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1806|1806]] [[:en:October 31|October 31]] ) – [[:en:Utamaro|Kitagawa Utamaro]] , an ukiyo-e artist (born [[:en:1753|1753]] ).
